# Feature: sage board — live roster with zones + ctx gauges.
Output ../assets/demo-board.gif
Output build/demo-board.txt
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Hide
Type "export PATH=$HOME/bin:$PATH NO_COLOR=1" Enter
Type "unset FORCE_COLOR 2>/dev/null" Enter
Type 'cd "$HOME/src/atlas" && clear' Enter
Show
Type "sage board"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
